\pard\fi-720\li720\tx220\tx720\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\tab\bullet\tab Drag almost any normal UI Panel (e.g. CharacterFrame, SpellbookFrame, TalentFrame, QuestLogFrame, FriendsFrame, etc.) from any open space on the frame. This movement is intended to be for temporary changes and does not store location in the FluidFrames database. \par
\tab\bullet\tab However, this movement registers the frame as user placed.  The position will be remembered by the WoW client and restored on subsequent login/reloadui if not overridden by placement code (e.g. CharacterFrame, Minimap). Most of these draggable frames reset if you hide and re-show them. \par
\tab\bullet\tab Some frames will not reset automatically (e.g. GameMenuFrame, BattlefieldFrame). To reset these, highlight the frame, right click to reset and then reloadui/relog.\par
\tab\bullet\tab The MinimapCluster is an added exception case and can be dragged by the top bar.\par
\tab\bullet\tab Temporary dragging can be disabled using the checkbox in the Khoas options.\par
